
#0: welcome to puppet for hackers quest.

#1: please join our slack for questions: https://cmw2016.slack.com/messages/p4h/

#2: use "quest" tool as root, which is meant to keep you busy ;)

    ( btw. it's the same tool that learning vm uses, so you might want to take a look afterwards: https://puppetlabs.com/download-learning-vm )

#3: put your code in /etc/puppetlabs/code/environments/production/modules/quest#{n}/ so our robot can assess it and give you some points.

#4: ask wonderful questions!

#5: give us a shout on twitter with #puppetizewarsaw!

happy hacking!

